text: Martin Hummervoll (born 13 March 1996) is a Norwegian footballer who plays as a forward for Fana IL. == Career == He made his first team debut in the 2014 Norwegian Football Cup, even scoring a goal against Sola. He later made his league debut against Start in September 2014, when he started the match on the left wing.
